om]], 5 [[Rudy Fern\u00e1ndez (basketball)|Rudy Fern\u00e1ndez]] '''(C)''', 8 [[Pau Ribas]], 9 [[Ricky Rubio]] '''([[FIBA Basketball World Cup Most Valuable Player|MVP]])''', 10 [[V\u00edctor Claver]], 13 [[Marc Gasol]], 14 [[Willy Hernang\u00f3mez]], 18 [[Pierre Oriola]], 22 [[Xavi Rabaseda]], 23 [[Sergio Llull]], 33 [[Javier Beir\u00e1n]], 41 [[Juan Hernang\u00f3mez]] (Coach: [[Sergio Scariolo]])\n\n==Players==\n*'''Bold''' denotes players still playing international basketball.\n{{updated|15 September 2019, including all friendly matches}}<ref>[http://www.seleccionbaloncesto.es/jugadores.aspx Spanish national team website]</ref>\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\n\n===Most capped players===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!#\n!style=\"width:160px;\"| Player\n!National career\n!Matches\n!Points\n|-\n| 1 || align=left|[[Juan Carlos Navarro (basketball)|Juan Carlos Navarro]] || 2000\u20132017 || '''253''' || 2801\n|-\n| 2 || align=left|[[Juan Antonio San Epifanio|Epi]] || 1979\u20131994 || '''239''' || 3330\n|-\n| 3 || align=left|[[Felipe Reyes]] || 2001\u20132016 || '''236''' || 1715\n|-\n| 4 || align=left|'''[[Rudy Fern\u00e1ndez (basketball)|Rudy Fern\u00e1ndez]]''' || 2004\u2013{{0}}{{0}}{{0}}{{0}} || '''224''' || 1915\n|-\n| 5 || align=left|[[Francisco Buscat\u00f3|Nino Buscat\u00f3]] || 1959\u20131973 || '''222''' || 1913\n|-\n| 6 || align=left|'''[[Pau Gasol]]''' || 2001\u2013{{0}}{{0}}{{0}}{{0}} || '''208''' || 3599\n|-\n| 7 || align=left|[[Jos\u00e9 Calder\u00f3n (basketball)|Jos\u00e9 Manuel Calder\u00f3n]] || 2002\u20132016 || '''193''' || 1233\n|-\n| 8 || align=left|[[Wayne Brabender]] || 1969\u20131982 || '''190''' || 2861\n|-\n| 9 || align=left|[[Josep Maria Margall]] || 1975\u20131988 || '''188''' || 1030\n|-\n| 10 || align=left|[[Andr\u00e9s Jim\u00e9nez Fern\u00e1ndez|Andr\u00e9s Jim\u00e9nez]] || 1982\u20131994 || '''187''' || 2393\n|}\n{{col-break}}\n\n===Top scorers===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-a