{"title_page": "Chief of Integrated Defence Staff", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=January 2020}}\n{{Infobox official post\n| post           = Chief of Integrated Defence Staff To The Chairman Chiefs Of Staff Committee (CISC)\n| flag           = \n| flagborder     = \n| flagsize       = \n| insignia       = \n| insigniaborder = yes\n| insigniasize   = \n| image        = File:Armed forces logo.png\n| imagesize      = 100px\n| incumbent      =\n| incumbentsince =\n| formation      =\n| first          = [[Lieutenant General]] Pankaj Joshi\n| last           = \n| website        = [https://www.ids.nic.in/cisc.php  Official Website]\n}}\n\n'''Chief of Integrated Defence Staff to the Chairman Chiefs of Staff Committee (CISC)''' was the head of the [[Integrated Defence Staff]] which acted as the point organisation for jointmanship in the [[Ministry of Defence (India)|Ministry of Defence]].\n\nThe CISC was a [[Three-star rank]] officer from the three Services in rotation. The CISC reported to the [[Chairman of the Chiefs of Staff Committee]] (Chairman COSC) in [[New Delhi]]. He was assisted by the following five Principal Staff Officers (all [[Three-star rank|three-star]] appointments) who headed the various branches within the IDS. \n\n* Deputy Chief of Integrated Defence Staff (Policy Planning and Force Development) - DCIDS (PP&FD) <ref>{{cite web |title=Integrated Defence Staff |url=https://www.ids.nic.in/dacids-pp-fd.php |website=www.ids.nic.in}}</ref>\t \n* Deputy Chief of Integrated Defence Staff (Doctrine, Organisation and Training) - DCIDS (DOT) <ref>{{cite web |title=Integrated Defence Staff |url=https://www.ids.nic.in/dacids-dot.php |website=www.ids.nic.in}}</ref>\n* Deputy Chief of Integrated Defence Staff (Operations) - DCIDS (Ops) <ref>{{cite web |title=Integrated Defence Staff |url=https://www.ids.nic.in/dacids-ops.php |website=www.ids.nic.in}}</ref>\n* Director General [[Defence Intelligence Agency (India)|Defence Intelligence Agency]] & Deputy Chief of Integrated Defence Staff (Intelligence) - DGDIA & DCIDS (Int) <ref>{{cite web |title=Integrated Defence Staff |url=https://www.ids.nic.in/dgdia-dcids.php |website=www.ids.nic.in}}</ref>\n* Deputy Chief of Integrated Defence Staff (Medical Branch) - DCIDS (Med) <ref>{{cite web |title=Integrated Defence Staff |url=https://www.ids.nic.in/dcids-med.php |website=www.ids.nic.in}}</ref>\n\nIn November 2019, government sources disclosed the post of Chief of Integrated Defence Staff would be converted to that of Vice Chief of Defence Staff when the post of [[Chief of Defence Staff (India)|Chief of Defence Staff]] is officially created in December.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/new-chief-of-defence-staff-will-direct-three-service-chiefs/story-r9sHOKiMmIoYemSlXODWPK.html|title=India\u2019s first Chief of Defence Staff will direct three service chiefs|first1=Shishir|last1=Gupta|work=Hindustan Times |accessdate=24 November 2019}}</ref>\n\nThe last CISC was [[Vice Admiral]] [[R. Hari Kumar]], [[Ati Vishisht Seva Medal|AVSM]], [[Vishisht Seva Medal|VSM]] who took over on 2 December 2019 as the 13th CISC.<ref>{{cite tweet|user=HQ_IDS_India|number=1201512924583358464|title=V Adm R Hari Kumar, AVSM, VSM assumed the Appt of CISC on 02 Dec 19.|date=2019-12-01}}</ref>\n\n== List of Chiefs of Integrated Defence Staff ==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|- style=\"background:#cccccc\"\n!{{Abbr|No.|Number}}\n!Name\n!Portrait\n!Branch\n!Assumed Office\n!Left Office\n!Reference(s)\n|-\n|1\n|[[Lieutenant General]] [[Pankaj Joshi (Army officer)|Pankaj Joshi]] {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|PVSM|AVSM}}}}\n|\n| rowspan=\"1\" |{{Army|India}}\n|{{Start date|2001|10|01|df=y}}\n|{{Start date|2003|09|30|df=y}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thehindu.com/thehindu/2001/10/02/stories/0102000c.htm|title=The Hindu : Pankaj Joshi is new CIDS|website=thehindu.com|access-date=2018-11-29}}</ref>\n|-\n|2\n|[[Vice Admiral]] [[Raman Puri]] {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|PVSM|AVSM|VSM}}}}\n|\n| rowspan=\"1\" |{{navy|India}}\n|{{Start date|2003|10|20|df=y}}\n|{{Start date|2006|02|28|df=y}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thehindu.com/2003/10/21/stories/2003102106601100.htm|title=Raman Puri takes over as CIDS|date=2003-10-21|accessdate=2019-01-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|3\n|[[Lieutenant General]] [[H. S. Lidder]] {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|UYSM|YSM|VSM}}}}\n|\n| rowspan=\"1\" |{{Army|India}}\n|{{Start date|2006|03|02|df=y}}\n|{{Start date|2008|09|31|df=y}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=24748|title=India will continue to strive towards achieving minimum deterrence - Antony|website=pib.nic.in|access-date=2018-11-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=39342|title=NDA Cadets Excel in World Arena|website=pib.nic.in|access-date=2018-11-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.oneindia.com/2006/03/02/lt-gen-hs-lidder-new-cids-1141380703.html|title=Lt Gen HS Lidder new CIDS|work=oneindia.com|access-date=2018-11-29|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|4\n|[[Air Marshal]] [[Suresh Chandra Mukul]] {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|AVSM|VM|VSM}}}}\n|\n|{{air force|India}}\n|{{Start date|2008|10|01|df=y}}\n|{{Start date|2010|12|30|df=y}}\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-kerala/Air-Marshal-S.C.-Mukul-bids-farewell/article15312886.ece|title=Air Marshal S.C. Mukul bids farewell|date=2008-09-29|work=The Hindu|access-date=2018-11-29|language=en-IN|issn=0971-751X}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lt Gen Nagal is new Strategic Forces commander|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/lt-gen-nagal-is-new-strategic-forces-commander/articleshow/3546079.cms|date=2008-09-30|accessdate=2018-12-01}}</ref>\n|-\n|5\n|[[Vice Admiral]] [[Devendra Kumar Joshi]] {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|AVSM|YSM|NM|VSM}}}}\n|[[File:DK Joshi official p