ib.nic.in|access-date=2018-11-29}}</ref>\n|-\n|9\n|[[Lieutenant General]] [[Anil Chait]] {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|PVSM|AVSM|VSM}}}}\n|[[File:Anil Chait CIDS.jpg|frameless|100x100px]]\n|{{Start date|2013|07|01|df=y}}\n|{{Start date|2014|06|30|df=y}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=96933|title=Lieutenant General Anil Chait Takes over as Chief of Integrated Defence Staff to CISC|website=pib.nic.in|access-date=2018-11-29}}</ref>\n|-\n|10\n|{{Small|[[Air Marshal]]}} P P Reddy {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|VM}}}}\n|[[File:P P Reddy CIDS.jpg|frameless|102x102px]]\n|{{air force|India}}\n|{{Start date|2014|07|01|df=y}}\n|{{Start date|2016|10|30|df=y}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=105972|title=Air Marshal PP Reddy Takes Over as CISC|website=pib.nic.in|access-date=2018-11-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/air-marshal-reddy-is-new-chief-of-integrated-defence-staff-114070100464_1.html|title=Air Marshal Reddy is new Chief of Integrated Defence Staff|last=IANS|date=2014-07-01|work=Business Standard India|access-date=2018-11-29}}</ref>\n|-\n|11\n|[[Lieutenant General]] [[Satish Dua]] {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|UYSM|SM|VSM}}}}\n|[[File:Satish Dua CISC.jpg|frameless|102x102px]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{Army|India}}\n|{{Start date|2016|10|31|df=y}}\n|{{Start date|2018|10|31|df=y}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=153225|title=Lt Gen Satish Dua takes over as CISC|website=pib.nic.in|access-date=2018-11-29}}</ref>\n|-\n|12\n|[[Lieutenant General]] [[Podali Shankar Rajeshwar|P. S. Rajeshwar]] {{small|{{postnominals|country=IND|sep=,|PVSM|AVSM}|VSM}}}}\n|[[File:Lt. Gen. P.S. Rajeshwar taking charge as the 12th Chief of Integrated Defence Staff to Chairman COSC, in New Delhi on November 01, 2018.JPG|frameless|100x100px]]\n|{{Start date|2018|11|01|df=y}}\n|{{Start date|2019|11|30|df=y}}\n